title: Paint de Sky with Start - The best of Enya
description:
Paint the Sky with Stars - The Best of Enya is a 1997 compilation album by Irish musician Enya featuring a selection of her best known material plus two previously unreleased tracks: "Paint the Sky with Stars" and "Only If...". It won the Japanese Grand Prix Album of the Year.
